#play +c+e+g+c+e+g#c
CAPTURE! The docking latches ring home.
Columbia and the LM are now one stack.
The way east is open to lunar orbit.
#end
:already
Docking capture confirmed. Fly east.
#end

    end
    stat at 8,10 element Object cycle 3 p1 cp437:0x9E under Empty color 0x00
    oop
@sun
#end
:touch
The Sun burns off your port side, small and
merciless. Do not stare. There is nothing
out here but distance and arithmetic.
#end

    end
    stat at 30,3 element Object cycle 7 p1 cp437:0x07 under Empty color 0x00
    oop
@drift
#end
:touch
#play s.c.e
Cislunar space. Weightless, silent, and
about a quarter million miles wide. The
Earth is a blue marble behind you; the Moon
a pale coin to the east.
Steer toward Columbia and dock before you
press onward.
#end

    end
  end
end

