stays warm upstairs.
$Ready to separate the Lunar Module?
!go;Release the docking latches.
!wait;Not yet. Run the checks again.
#end
:wait
Prudent. Descent is unforgiving. Touch
me again when your nerve returns.
#end
:go
#play tcegtcegtc#e
#zap touch
CAPCOM: Eagle, you are go for undocking.
The latches release with a soft thump,
and Columbia drifts silently away above
the gray horizon. The descent passage is
open below you.
#end
:touch
The Eagle floats free, tethered to
nothing but gravity now. Step onto the
descent stage south of here.
#end

